OL,3,CArchive footage from 1960s shows
OL,4,CTorbay in its tourism heyday
OL,6,FBikinis on the beach, classic car
OL,7,Fshows, families building sandcastles
OL,8,Fand waiters racing each other through
OL,9,Fthe streets.
OL,11,FArchive footage from 1968 shows Torbay
OL,12,Fin its tourism heyday, a stark
OL,13,Fcontrast to the struggles felt by many
OL,14,Fin the industry in 2024.
OL,16,FHotel and guest house owners have told
OL,17,FITV West Country they are fighting for
OL,18,Fsurvival thanks to the cost of living
OL,19,Fcrisis. But 50 years ago it was all so
OL,20,Fdifferent.
